parameters.name: DBInstanceId
parameters.description:
The cluster ID.

> You can call the [DescribeDBInstances](~~86911~~) operation to query the information about all AnalyticDB for PostgreSQL instances within a region, including instance IDs.

parameters.name: VSwitchId
parameters.description:
The vSwitch ID.

>   The zone where the **vSwitch** resides must be the same as the zone that is specified by **ZoneId**.

parameters.name: ZoneId
parameters.description:
The zone ID.

> You can call the [DescribeRegions](~~86912~~) operation to query the available regions and zones.
